00:00:01.859 --> 00:00:06.690
hello welcome today we will prepare chicken tinga

00:00:06.690 --> 00:00:08.669
these are the ingredients

00:00:08.669 --> 00:00:14.079
three quarters of a kilo of chicken breast, three quarters of a kilo of onion

00:00:14.079 --> 00:00:19.919
three quarters of a kilo of jitomates or ripe tomatoes, three cloves of garlic

00:00:19.919 --> 00:00:23.319
Marinated five canned chipotle chilies

00:00:23.319 --> 00:00:24.470
Pepper

00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:26.089
and salt to taste

00:00:26.089 --> 00:00:33.089
First, wash the breast and boil for 30 minutes in two liters of water,

00:00:33.199 --> 00:00:38.520
a teaspoon of salt, a piece of onion, a clove of garlic

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:40.920
and optionally a sheet

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.910
laurel

00:00:42.910 --> 00:00:49.910
expect it to cool, crumble the chicken, and reserved

00:00:50.430 --> 00:00:55.450
we chop the onions in julienne or half moon

00:00:55.450 --> 00:01:00.120
in a hot pan put 4 tablespoons oil

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:02.690
add the onion diced

00:01:02.690 --> 00:01:08.390
and fry over medium heat until translucent

00:01:08.390 --> 00:01:12.910
in a blender put the tomatoes, 2 cloves of garlic

00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:15.120
a piece of onion

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:18.010
marinated chipotle peppers and grind

00:01:18.010 --> 00:01:23.710
add it to the pan with minced onions

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.560
stir

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:31.300
cover and let simmer for five minutes over medium heat

00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:32.960
uncover

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:36.410
add the chicken

00:01:36.410 --> 00:01:41.160
season with pepper and a teaspoon of salt

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:46.280
stir all ingredients and rectify the salt

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:49.280
cook uncovered over medium heat

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.790
until all liquid evaporates

00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:56.210
shut it off and let rest for 10 minutes

00:01:56.210 --> 00:02:02.260
ready, it only remains to serve and enjoy our chicken tinga

